## Write a program to print numbers from 1 to n

```
Input  : 5
Output : 1 2 3 4 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="print-numbers-from-1-to-n" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main()
{
    int number, i;
    printf("Input: ");
    scanf("%d", &number);
    for (i = 1; i <= number; ++i)
    {
        printf("%d", i);
    }
    return 0;
}
```

```cpp
